headline: Costco Returns. The Stock’s Technicals Are Improving, Fast
summary: For much of the past year,  Costco Wholesale  has done little to excite investors.  After a powerful multiyear run, the stock spent 2025 receding as momentum cooled and leadership rotated elsewhere.  Recent price action suggests Costco may be transitioning back to accumulation, helped in part by strong December sales data.
